data.description: Move right in to this easy-living community with all appliances included, you're all set! Quaint porch welcomes friends and family. Hardwood floors grace the entire main level (except laundry). Inside enjoy a beautifully updated powder bath and kitchen with quartz and butcher block counters, painted cabinets, updated lighting and hardware, and all stainless appliances. Eating area is huge, with ample space for beverage carts or bonus cabinets. Main level living room includes wood floors and a slider door to patio / yard area. As one of the larger 2-story plans in the community, enjoy bonus family room/loft (and owners are happy to leave large sectional couch). Three bedrooms are up, and 2 baths... the owner's suite has a walk-in closet and luxuriously upgraded shower and double vanity. The community includes alley load garages, small fenced yards, and quick access to Marksheffel for easy commutes to local military installations, and the Powers corridor for dining and shopping!
